response.original_title: The Lost Art of Cadaver Collecting
response.overview: Voglio Spanel is one of the last remaining cadaver collectors of his profession. But, it's getting increasingly more difficult to be in his line of work in today's climate. The people in his life share their opinions of him as he searches for love...and faces the consequences.
response.tagline: He's either a genius...or deeply disturbed
response.title: The Lost Art of Cadaver Collecting
